---
title: Cal Smart Southwest Turkey and Poblano Skillet with Charred Corn Wild Rice and Pico de Gallo
description: This gorgeous Southwest-inspired skillet takes things to the next level with a bed of smoky, charred corn tossed with a wild rice medley and topped with spiced turkey. Poblanos offer a mild heat that's tempered by the pico de gallo!
